value.0: The plant where the ever-popular sweetberries grow. Fairly small-sized, these plants have been actually known to grow to larger sizes as house plants, although this practice is rather uncommon. Perhaps due to the fey that usually bother the houses which have the plants potted...

The Sweetberry is a highly prized item for Cordorian children, to others, completely useless.  Commonly stuck on the end of a stick and licked, the sweetberry has a powerfully sweet taste that most adults find overwhelming.  Except in Amia, where they are enjoyed by almost all, sometimes even a little too much, in the case of an ex-assassin who craves them with a passion.

Value.value: If you accept and make a blood oath here and now, you swear to serve the court of dreams, the Seelie Fey. This means you support and aid the Court of Dreams. You defend and protect all that holds beauty and support a persons dreams, making sure they do not give up on them. While you respect both sides of the balance, you yourself work for the light, the summer, the beautiful dream.
